org.fax4j.spi.http

Class HTTPRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fax4j.spi.http.HTTPRequest

  • public class HTTPRequest
extends Object
    Holds the HTTP request data used to send the fax data to the web server.
    This class is not thread safe.

    0.1
    Version:
    1.02
    Author:
